data.description: Private Oasis located in the most sought-after section of Northwood Shores. This updated 3BR/2BTH Midcentury Modern home has been meticulously updated while maintaining its original Old Florida charm. The paver circular drive welcomes guests into a bright and open living room with vaulted ceilings, dining area and sunroom with immediate views of the pool and lushly landscaped, fenced-in backyard. Glistening hardwood floors throughout and newly installed impact French doors bring in the outdoors & sunlight. Perfect for entertaining, the gourmet kitchen offers stainless steel appliances, cherry wood cabinets, granite counter tops and travertine flooring. With a split floor plan, the primary bedroom offers privacy, 2 closets and an ensuite bathroom. The gracious living area continues out into the deep backyard with fruit trees, an oversized, resurfaced 34-foot pool, and a newly renovated 300 sq ft pool cabana with kitchenette, full bath, and murphy bed. This lovely home is a must see and only minutes to Northwood Village, Palm Beach Island, Downtown and PB International Airport.
